<p>We may use third-party advertising companies to serve ads when you are on the website. The companies use non-personally identifiable information about your visits to this and other websites to provide ads about goods and services of potential interest to you. ConnectingSingles.com does not have access to or control of the cookies that may be placed by the third-party ad servers. Non-personally identifiable demographic information may also be shared for survey purposes.</p>
