<p>Be aware that any personally identifiable information you choose to disclose on this site, in public on your profile or forum, public chat or blog entries, or in private through email or private chat (IM) to other members, is done at your own risk and that it may be collected or used by others. Caution and good sense should always be used in disclosing your personal identity to others and in selecting the type of information that you post on the website or release to others. ConnectingSingles.com is not responsible for the use of any personal information that you may choose to disclose while on or off the website.</p>
